import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { Member } from '../entity/member'; @Component({ selector: 'app-register', templateUrl: './register.component.html', styleUrls: ['./register.component.css'], }) export class RegisterComponent { showForgetPasswordContent = false; memberData: Member = { memberId: 0, firstName: '', lastName: '', email: '', password: '', forgetPasswordAnswer: '', mobileNo: '', }; onSubmit() { console.log(this.memberData); this.showForgetPasswordContent = true; } showForgetPassword() { } }
First Name is required
Last Name is required
Email is required
Pattern should be john@example.com
Password is required
Password must be at least 8 characters
1 UpperCase, 1 LowerCase Latter and Also Contain Number
Last Name is required
Mobile Number Should Have proper Formate
Mobile Number Should Have proper Formate

Forget Password Answer is required
